|CKBCharlatan Help: The Index Nobody Swears Is Complete|000

Syntax: charlhelp [topic|command]
Alias:  chelp

Useful entries in the Confidence's little black book:

  intro       Who the Confidence claims to be
  commands    Every trick currently admitted into evidence
  abilities   A guided tour of the dangerous pockets
  roads       Misdirection, Volatility, and Contraband
  schemes     Rank 35+ cons, cloak notes, and active loadouts
  chat        Etiquette for the Charlatan line, allegedly
  members     The Confidence's active roll

You can also ask about a trick by name:

  charlhelp confuse
  charlhelp brewacid
  charlhelp brewelement
  charlhelp cookash
  charlhelp loadweapon
  charlhelp schemes

If a crossed-out entry disagrees with 'chskills', trust the cloak. The cloak
is newer, armed, and standing closer to you.
